This torrent is 1.0.0.0, you can check by right-clicking on "MOHW.exe" > Properties > Details. You can just paste a 1.0.0.2 crack into 1.0.0.0 game's dir and the game will launch by clicking on "MOHW.exe". However, it makes more sense and is recommended to first update the game to 1.0.0.2 and then crack it. You should experience less crashes this way. Updating and cracking is the same procedure, just paste files into game dir, replace those with same filename. There have been quite a few cracks released, choose one that works best for you (btw, that link now has 3 cracks). If the game crashes, try another crack or try reducing graphics settings.
